<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2609330>
    dc:description "FIGURES 18–24. Aprostocetus chilophagae: 18, female, lateral view; 19, female, dorsal view; 20, male, lateral view; 21, male, genitalia" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2609330/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2609328>
    dc:description "FIGURES 16–17. Male, Aprostocetus nebraskensis: 16, body, dorso-lateral view (South Dakota); 17, mesoscutellum, dorsellum and part of propodeum, dorsal view (South Dakota)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2609328/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2609318>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–4. Antennae of female Aprostocetus bromi (Kostjukov) and A. nebraskensis (Girault): 1, A. bromi (Kostjukov) (Paratype, ZISP); 2, A. bromi reared from Stenodiplosis bromicola on Bromus inermis (South Dakota); 3, A. bromi reared from Stenodiplosis spartinae on Spartina pectinata (South Dakota); 4, Antenna of A. nebraskensis (Girault) (Type USNM)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2609318/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

